{"tid":1877231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年2月13日 — 早晨，Twitter戰線須要大家","createTime":"2020-02-13T01:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T15:41:35.000Z","uid":253983,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"36fe9f560b7fbb396849b376f3e2b3cea4b0a40d","tid":1877231,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"我地依家係面對緊 抗爭 同 抗疫兩條戰線<br />\nGreat challenges ahead，我地更要保持鎮定但唔麻木<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線好重要，我地要維持同全世界聯繫<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個今日任務嘅匯集，大家可以㩒呢條link入今日嘅任務<br />\n記得 Like + Retweet <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原Tweet</span></span> 呀 <br />\n(總係有朋友仔Like + Tweet我地個comment就算，係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">㩒入去原Tweet先Like + Retweet</span></span>呀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1227761080988061696?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1227761080988061696%3Fs%3D21&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9883b294\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1227761080988061696%3Fs%3D21&h=890431b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1227761080988061696?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，本站現新增簽名戰線，附上各項聯署任務，歡迎各位加入<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎大家follow本站Twitter，留意每日Twitter戰線任務<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3e334f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a>"},{"pid":"fb794a7053c87dcee4f0f5484088056c30977fba","tid":1877231,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12813fe729df0eac6415cb3fdcdd37bab2eb06d5","tid":1877231,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:08:12.